<body>
	<p>
		Hello <%= data.firstName %>, <br />
	</p>
	<p>
		We recently received a request for a forgotten password. To change your Delivery APP password and login again to our platform, please click below:
	</p>
	<p>
		<a href="<%=data.link %>" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
	</p>
	<p>
		If you did not request this change, you do not need to do anything.
	</p>
	<p>
		If you can't get the button to work, you can paste this link into your browser: <%=data.link%>
	</p>
</body>